pageContext.claim: “We've reduced the number of unemployed veterans by nearly 50 percent. … And veteran unemployment is now at the lowest level ever, ever, ever recorded.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump's claim does not add up. The unemployment rate for veterans was lower in 2000, according to the Bureau of Labor Statistics. "The jobless rate for all veterans was little changed at 3.5 percent in 2018," BLS reported.
